    <entry>
      <title>Git连接异常处理</title>
      <link href="/2026/01/28/buildproblem1/"/>
      <url>/2026/01/28/buildproblem1/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h1><p>在国内使用Git等外网总会出现各种连接异常，即便挂了VPN（注意科学上网）也总是还是会出现连接问题<br>例如在<code>hexo d</code>步骤时候出现如下报错：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">fatal: unable to access <span class="string">&#x27;https://github.com/xxx/xxx.github.io.git/&#x27;</span>: Failed to connect to github.com port 443 via 127.0.0.1 after 2111 ms: Could not connect to server</span><br><span class="line">FATAL Something<span class="string">&#x27;s wrong. Maybe you can find the solution here: https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Error: Spawn failed</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at ChildProcess.&lt;anonymous&gt; (D:\xxx\xxx\node_modules\.store\hexo-util@2.7.0\node_modules\hexo-util\lib\spawn.js:51:21) </span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at ChildProcess.emit (node:events:508:28)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at cp.emit (D:\xxx\xxx\node_modules\.store\cross-spawn@7.0.6\node_modules\cross-spawn\lib\enoent.js:34:29)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">    at ChildProcess._handle.onexit (node:internal/child_process:294:12)</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>往往说明<code>网络连接异常</code><br>我们需要手动调整Git的网络代理接口</p><h1 id="查看自己的服务器代理接口"><a href="#查看自己的服务器代理接口" class="headerlink" title="查看自己的服务器代理接口"></a>查看自己的服务器代理接口</h1><p>1.打开自己的控制面板并点击<code>网络与Internet</code>选项<br><img src="/imgs/blog_img/prob1.png"><br>2.再点击<code>Internet选项</code>进入<code>Internet属性</code>界面<br><img src="/imgs/blog_img/prob2.png"><br>3.选择<code>连接</code>卡片，再点击<code>局域网设置</code><br><img src="/imgs/blog_img/prob3.png"><br>由此可以查看到<code>代理服务器</code>的<code>地址</code>和<code>端口</code></p><h1 id="更改Git代理接口"><a href="#更改Git代理接口" class="headerlink" title="更改Git代理接口"></a>更改Git代理接口</h1><p>在Git bash中输入</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">#以我的为例，具体的要看自己的代理服务器</span></span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:32210</span><br><span class="line">$ git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:32210</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>完成之后<code>hexo d</code>步骤会非常顺畅</p>]]></content>
      
      
